From the Yuan you, an old Chinese commentary on the Numogram (translated by David Hawkes):
"I toured the Four Outlands,
Traversed the Six Regions,
Up to the lightning's fissure,
And down to the Great Abyss."
Among the greatest memes ever, it's true.
